
This is the Perl distribution Class-Value-URI.

## Installation

Class-Value-URI installation is straightforward.
If your CPAN shell is set up, you should just be able to do

    % cpan Class::Value::URI

Download it, unpack it, then build it as per the usual:

    % perl Makefile.PL
    % make && make test

Then install it:

    % make install

## Documentation

Class-Value-URI documentation is available as in POD.
So you can do:

    % perldoc Class::Value::URI

to read the documentation with your favorite pager.
